===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˌvaɪəˈlɪn/}}, {{SAMPA|/vaI@lIn/}}
* {{audio|en-us-violin.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|ɪn}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{musical instrument}} A musical four-string [[instrument]], generally played with a [[bow]] or by plucking the string.  Pitch is set by pressing the strings at the appropriate place with the fingers.
#: ''The first '''violin''' often plays the lead melody lines in a string quartet.''

